{
    "T04sanss16u:0": " bhadracaryāvidhiḥ ṣoḍaśaḥ paricchedaḥ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:1": " idānīṃ trayāṇām api vṛddhir vā-",
    "T04sanss16u:2": " [ Cambridge MS f119a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:3": " cyā ||",
    "T04sanss16u:4": " kim arthaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:5": " grahītāraḥ subahavaḥ svalpaṃ cêdam anena kiṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:6": " na câtitṛptijanakaṃ vardhanīyam idaṃ tataḥ ||atitṛpti buddhatvaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:7": " tan na śrāvakasādhāraṇena śuddhimātreṇa satvānāṃ janyatae ity arthaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:8": " ātmabhāvasya kā vṛddhir balânālasya vardhanaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:9": " [ Bendall ed p274 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:10": " tatrâryaratnameghe balam uktaṃ |na sa satvaḥ satvanikāye saṃvidyate yo bodhisatvasya balena balaṃ mardayed ity ādi ||",
    "T04sanss16u:11": " tasya kathaṃ vardhanam |",
    "T04sanss16u:12": " yad uktam āryatathāgataguhyasūtre āryavajrapāṇer baladarśanavismitâjātaśatrupṛṣṭena bhagavatā",
    "T04sanss16u:13": " daśabhir mahārāja dharmaiḥ samanvāgato bodhisatvâivaṃrūpāṃ balavattāṃ pratilabhate |katamair daśabhiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:14": " iha mahārāja bodhisatvaḥ kāyaṃ jīvitaṃ ca parityajati |",
    "T04sanss16u:15": " na ca punaḥ saddharmaṃ parityajati |",
    "T04sanss16u:16": " sarvasatvānāṃ câvanamati na ca punar mānaṃ bṛṃhayati |",
    "T04sanss16u:17": " durbalānāṃ ca satvānāṃ kṣamate |",
    "T04sanss16u:18": " na pratighaṃ karoti |",
    "T04sanss16u:19": " jighatsitānāṃ ca satvānām agraṃ varabhojanaṃ dadāti |",
    "T04sanss16u:20": " bhītānāṃ ca satvānām abhayaṃ dadāti |",
    "T04sanss16u:21": " glānānāṃ ca satvānāṃ bhūtacikitsāyai utsuko bhavati |",
    "T04sanss16u:22": " daridrāṃś ca satvān bhogaiḥ saṃtarpayati |",
    "T04sanss16u:23": " tathāgatacaitye ca sudhāpiṇḍalepanaṃ karoti |",
    "T04sanss16u:24": " ānandavacanaṃ satvānāṃ śrāvayati |",
    "T04sanss16u:25": " daridraduṣkhitānāṃ ca satvānāṃ bhogasaṃvibhāgaṃ karoti |",
    "T04sanss16u:26": " śrāntaklāntānāṃ ca satvānāṃ bhāraṃ vahati |",
    "T04sanss16u:27": " ebhir mahārāja daśabhir iti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:28": " [ Bendall ed p275 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:29": " anālasyavardhanaṃ katamat |",
    "T04sanss16u:30": " yad vīryavardhanaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:31": " yathôktaṃ sāgaramatisūtre |",
    "T04sanss16u:32": " ārabdhavīryeṇa sāgaramate bodhisatvena bhavitavyaṃ sadā dṛḍhaparākrameṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:33": " tīvracchandena bodhisatvena bhavitavyam anikṣiptadhureṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:34": " ārabdhavīryāṇāṃ hi sāgaramate bodhisatvānāṃ na durlabhā bhavaty anuttarā samyaksaṃbodhiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:35": " tat kasya hetoḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:36": " yatra sāgaramate vīryaṃ tatra bodhiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:37": " kusīdānāṃ punaḥ sudūravidūre bodhiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:38": " nâsti kusīdasya dānaṃ yāvan nâsti prajñā",
    "T04sanss16u:39": " [ Cambridge MS f120a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:40": " nâsti kusīdasya parârthêti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:41": " candrapradīpasūtre 'py āha |",
    "T04sanss16u:42": " utpalaṃ vārimadhye vā so 'nupūrveṇa vardhatae |ity ādi ||",
    "T04sanss16u:43": " iyaṃ saṃkṣepād ātmabhāvavṛddhiḥ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:44": " śūnyatā karuṇāgarbhād dānād bhogasya vardhanaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:45": " yathôktaṃ vajracchedikāyāṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:46": " yo bodhisatvo 'pratiṣṭhito dānaṃ dadāti |",
    "T04sanss16u:47": " tasya puṇyaskandhasya na sukaraṃ pramāṇam udgrahītum iti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:48": " mahatyām api prajñāpāramitāyām uktaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:49": " punar aparaṃ śāriputra bodhisatvena mahāsatvenâlpam api dānaṃ dadatā sarvasatveṣu sarvâkārajñatāyām upāyakauśalyapariṇāmanatāyām aprameyam asaṃkhyeyaṃ kartukāmena prajñāpāramitāyāṃ śikṣitavyam tathā sarvasatvānāṃ manorathān paripūrayitukāmena |",
    "T04sanss16u:50": " yāvaj jātarūparajatôdyānarājyâdibhir upakaraṇaiḥ prajñāpāramitāyāṃ śikṣitavyam iti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:51": " [ Bendall ed p276 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:52": " vinā ca karuṇayā na bodhisatvānāṃ kiṃcic ceṣṭitam iti vakṣyāmaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:53": " iti saṃkṣepād bhogavṛddhiḥ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:54": " puṇyavṛddhiḥ sarvavṛddhīnāṃ mūlam iti tadarthaṃ parikarabandhôcyate ||",
    "T04sanss16u:55": " kṛtvâdāv eva yatnena vyavasāyâśāyau dṛḍhau |",
    "T04sanss16u:56": " karuṇāṃ ca puraskṛtya yateta śubhavṛddhaye ||",
    "T04sanss16u:57": " cittaśuddhikālabhāvitānāṃ vyavasāyâdīnāṃ prayogârambhe punar āmukhīkaraṇena dṛḍhatâpādanârthaḥ ślokaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:58": " kṛtvêty ādipūrvakâiva ||",
    "T04sanss16u:59": " āsannayuddhakālānāṃ astrakauśalyâdaravat prayogasamakālaṃ dṛḍhīkariṣyāmîti",
    "T04sanss16u:60": " śaithilyanivāraṇârtham ādigrahaṇam |",
    "T04sanss16u:61": " tatra kathaṃ vyavasāyaṃ dṛḍhīkaroti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:62": " yathâryasudhanâryamaitreyam upasaṃprakrāntaḥ samyakcaryāniḥsamarthaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:63": " pūrvântakoṭīgatakāyapraṇāmaḥ kāyasamanvāhāreṇa kāyabalaṃ dṛḍhīkurvāṇaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:64": " pūrvântakoṭīgatakāya cittapariśuddhiniṣkāraṇasāṃsārikacittapracārasamanvāhāreṇa cittamanasikāraṃ nigṛhṇan |",
    "T04sanss16u:65": " pūrvântakoṭy-asa-",
    "T04sanss16u:66": " [ Bendall ed p277 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:67": " tkarmalaukikakāryaprayuktaniṣprayojanaparisyandasamanvāhāreṇa pratyutpannaprayojanamahāsāmarthyaṃ vicintayan |",
    "T04sanss16u:68": " pūrvântâbhūtaparikalpasamutthitavitathasaṃkalpasaṃdarśita-",
    "T04sanss16u:69": " [ Cambridge MS f120b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:70": " manasikārasamanvāhāreṇa sarvabodhisatvacaryāsamyaksaṃkalpâbhisaṃskārabalaṃ samutthāpayan |",
    "T04sanss16u:71": " atītâtmabhāvârthaprayogârambhaviṣamatāsamanvāhāreṇa sarvasatvârambhavaiśeṣikatayâdhyāśayabalaṃ dṛḍhīkurvāṇaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:72": " atītakāyasamudācāranirāsvādatāsamanvāhāreṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:73": " sarvabuddhadharmapratilābhaprayogamahâśvāsapratilābhêndriyavegān vivardhayamāno 'tītâdhvaviparyāsaprayuktamithyâśayaprayogasamanvāh-reṇa",
    "T04sanss16u:74": " pratyutpannâdhvasamyagdarśanâviparyāsasaṃprayuktena bodhisatvapraṇidhānasamādānena saṃtatiṃ pariśodhayan |",
    "T04sanss16u:75": " pūrvântagatâyogavīryârambhakāryâpariniṣpannâryasamādānasamanvāhāreṇa",
    "T04sanss16u:76": " pratyutpannabuddhadharmasamudāgamapratyupasthānena mahāvīryârambhavikrameṇa kāyacittasaṃpragrahaṃ saṃjanayamānaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:77": " pūrvântakoṭīpañcagatyapāyanikṣiptâtmaparanirupakaraṇâkhyanirupajīvyasamucchrayaparigrahasamanvāhāreṇa",
    "T04sanss16u:78": " sarvabuddhadharmôtthāpakasarvajagadupajīvyasarvakalyāṇamitrârāgaṇasamarthyâtmabhāvaparigrahaṇatayā",
    "T04sanss16u:79": " vipulaprītiprāmodyavegān vivardhayamānaḥ pratyutpannajanmâbhinirvṛttaṃ jarāvyādhimaraṇaśokâkarabhūtaṃ saṃyogaviyoganidhānabhūtaṃ samucchrayaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:80": " aparântakalpakoṭīgatabodhisatvacaryâcaraṇaprayuktasya satvaparipācanabuddhadharmaparigrahaprayuktasya",
    "T04sanss16u:81": " [ Bendall ed p278 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:82": " buddhakṣetrânucaraṇasarvadharmabhāṇakôpasthānasarvatathāgataśāsanasamanvāharaṇaprayuktasya",
    "T04sanss16u:83": " sarvadharmaparyeṣṭisahāyabhūtasya sarvakalyāṇamitradarśanasarvabuddhadharmasamudānayanaprayuktasya bodhisatvapraṇidhijñānaśarīrasya hetupratyayabhūtam avalokyâcintyakuśalamūlêndriyavegān viva",
    "T04sanss16u:84": " rdhayamānêti |",
    "T04sanss16u:85": " āryâkṣayamatinirdeśe mahāyānasūtre 'py uktaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:86": " eko bodhisatvo 'dvitīyo 'sahāyo 'nuttarāyāṃ samyaksaṃbodhau",
    "T04sanss16u:87": " [ Cambridge MS f121a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:88": " saṃnāhaṃ saṃnahyati |",
    "T04sanss16u:89": " sa vīryabalaparigṛhītenâdhyāśayenâparâvakāśâsvayaṃkārī |",
    "T04sanss16u:90": " svabalabalôdgataḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:91": " sâivaṃ dṛḍhasaṃnāhaḥ saṃnaddho |",
    "T04sanss16u:92": " yat kiñcit sarvasatvānāṃ pariprāpayitavyaṃ bhaviṣyati tad ahaṃ pariprāpayiṣyāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:93": " yat sarvâryāḥ sarvanavayānasaṃprasthitā bodhisatvā na pariprāpayiṣyanti tad ahaṃ pariprāpayiṣyāmi",
    "T04sanss16u:94": " na mama dānaṃ sahāyakaṃ |ahaṃ punar dānasya sahāyaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:95": " na mama śīlakṣāntivīryadhyānaprajñāḥ sahāyikāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:96": " ahaṃ punaḥ śīlakṣāntivīryadhyānaprajñānāṃ sahāyo |",
    "T04sanss16u:97": " nâhaṃ pāramitābhir upasthātavyo mayā punaḥ pāramitôpasthātavyāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:98": " evaṃ saṃgrahavastuṣu sarvakuśalamūleṣu caleyam |",
    "T04sanss16u:99": " yāvad ekākinā mayâdvitīyenâsahāyena vajramaye mahīmaṇḍale sthitena sabalaṃ savāhanaṃ māraṃ dharṣayitvâikacittakṣaṇasamâyuktayā prajñayânuttarā samyaksaṃbodhir abhisaṃboddhavyêti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:100": " āryavajradhvajasūtre 'py āha |",
    "T04sanss16u:101": " tad yathâpi nāma sūryo devaputrôdayamāno na tiṣṭhati |",
    "T04sanss16u:102": " jā-",
    "T04sanss16u:103": " [ Bendall ed p279 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:104": " tyandhadoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:105": " na tiṣṭhati gandharvanagaradoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:106": " na tiṣṭhati caturdvīpalokadhātubhūmirajodoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:107": " na tiṣṭhati rāhvasurêndradoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:108": " na tiṣṭhati dhūmamaṇḍaladoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:109": " na tiṣṭhati jambūdvīpakleśadoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:110": " na tiṣṭhati nānāchāyādoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:111": " na tiṣṭhati viṣamaparvatadoṣeṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:112": " evam eva bodhisatvo mahāsatvaḥ smṛtisaṃprajanyavipulagambhīracetâdīnasatvo guṇacaryājñānacaryâvasānaṃ yāvan na vivartate satvadrauhilyadoṣaiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:113": " na vipravasati kuśalamūlapariṇāmaiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:114": " satvadṛṣṭikāluṣyadoṣair na vivartate |",
    "T04sanss16u:115": " satvakṣobhacetobhir na dūrībhavati |",
    "T04sanss16u:116": " satvavinaṣṭasaṃtatyā bodhisaṃnāhaṃ na viṣkambhayati |",
    "T04sanss16u:117": " sarvajagatparitrāṇapraṇidhānasya satvakalikaluṣair na sraṃsanāṃ karoti yāvad bālaja-",
    "T04sanss16u:118": " [ Bendall ed p280 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:119": " nasamavadhānena |",
    "T04sanss16u:120": " na nirvidyate parasatvadoṣaiś ca |",
    "T04sanss16u:121": " tat kasya hetoḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:122": " anāvaraṇa-",
    "T04sanss16u:123": " [ Cambridge MS f121b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:124": " maṇḍalam etad udayati |",
    "T04sanss16u:125": " yad uta sarvajagadviśuddhivinayāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:126": " pe ||",
    "T04sanss16u:127": " yaś ca teṣāṃ sarvasatvānāṃ duṣkhaskandho vividhaṃ câvaraṇīyaṃ karma samutthitaṃ yena te āvaraṇīyena karmaṇā buddhān na paśyanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:128": " dharmaṃ na śṛṇvanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:129": " saṃghaṃ na jānanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:130": " tad ahaṃ teṣāṃ trividham āvaraṇīyaṃ karmôpacitaṃ duṣkhaskandhena svakena śarīreṇôpādadāmi tāsu tāsu narakôpapattiṣv apāyabhūmiṣu saṃvāseṣu ca |",
    "T04sanss16u:131": " te ca sarvasatvās tataś cyavantāṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:132": " ahaṃ ca duṣkhôpādānam upādadāmi vyavasyāmy utsahe |",
    "T04sanss16u:133": " na nivarte na palāyāmi nôttrasyāmi na saṃtrasyāmi na bibhemi na pratyudāvarte na viṣīdāmi",
    "T04sanss16u:134": " tat kasya hetoḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:135": " avaśyaṃ nirvāhayitavyo mayā sarvasatvānāṃ bhāro |",
    "T04sanss16u:136": " nâiṣa mama kāmakāraḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:137": " sarvasatvôttāraṇapraṇidhānaṃ mama |",
    "T04sanss16u:138": " mayā sarvasatvāḥ parimocayitavyā |",
    "T04sanss16u:139": " mayā sarvajagat samuttārayitavyaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:140": " jātikāntārāj jarākāntārād vyādhikāntārāc cyutyupapatikāntārāt sarvâpattikāntārāt sarvâpāyakāntārāt sarvasaṃsārakāntārāt sarvadṛṣṭigahanakāntārāt kuśaladharmapraṇāśakāntārād ajñānasamutthitakāntārāt tad ete mayā sarvasatvāḥ sarvakāntārebhyaḥ parimocayitavyāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:141": " tṛṣṇājālasaktâvidyānivaraṇâvṛtā bhavatṛṣṇāsaṃprayuktāḥ praṇāśaparyavasānā duṣkhapañjaraprakṣiptāś cārakasaṃniśritā |",
    "T04sanss16u:142": " abudhāḥ pratijñāviruddhāḥ saṃśayabhūtāḥ sadā vimatayo 'kṣemadarśinaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:143": " aniḥśaraṇakuśalā bhavârṇave āvartamaṇḍalâikacaraṇāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:144": " pe ||",
    "T04sanss16u:145": " sarvasatvānām anuttarajñānarājyapratiṣṭhāpanârtham ahaṃ carāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:146": " nâhaṃ kevalam ātmaparimocanâbhiyuktaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:147": " sarvasatvā hy ete mayā sarvajñatācittaplavena saṃsāradurgād dhartavyā |",
    "T04sanss16u:148": " mahāprapātād abhyutkṣeptavyāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:149": " sarvôpadravebhyaḥ parimocayitavyāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:150": " saṃsārasrotasaḥ pratārayitavyâtmanā mayā sarvasatvadu-",
    "T04sanss16u:151": " [ Cambridge MS f122a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:152": " ṣkhaskandho 'dhyavasitaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:153": " yāvad utsahe 'haṃ sarvâpāyeṣu sarvalokadhātuparyāpanneṣu sarvaduṣkhavāsam",
    "T04sanss16u:154": " anubhavitum |",
    "T04sanss16u:155": " na ca mayā sarvasatvāḥ kuśala-",
    "T04sanss16u:156": " [ Bendall ed p281 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:157": " mūlair vañcitavyāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:158": " vyavasyāmy aham ekâikasminn apāye 'parântakoṭīgatān kalpān saṃvasayituṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:159": " yathā câikâpāye tathā sarvâpāyaniravaśeṣasarvalokadhātuparyāpanneṣu sarvasatvaparimocananidānaṃ |tat kasya hetoḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:160": " varaṃ khalu punar aham eko duṣkhitaḥ syāṃ na cême sarvasatvāḥ apāyabhūmiprapatitāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:161": " mayā tatrâtmā bandhako dātavyaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:162": " sarvajagac ca niḥkretavyaṃ narakatiryagyoniyamalokakāntārād ahaṃ ca sarvasatvānām arthāya sarvaduṣkhavedanāskandham anena svakena śarīreṇânubhaveyam |",
    "T04sanss16u:163": " sarvasatvanidānam ahaṃ ca sarvasatvānāṃ prātibhāvyam utsahe satyavādī pratyayito 'visaṃvādakaḥ",
    "T04sanss16u:164": " na ca mayā sarvasatvāḥ parityaktāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:165": " tat kasya hetoḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:166": " sarvasatvârambaṇo mama sarvajñatācittôtpādôtpanno yad uta sarvajagatparimocanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:167": " na câhaṃ ratikāmatayânuttarāyāṃ samyaksaṃbodhau saṃprasthito nâpi pañcakāmaguṇaratyanubhavanāya nâpi kāmaviṣayaniṣevaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:168": " na câham anyonyakāmadhātuparyāpannarativyūhasamudānayanāya carāmi bodhisatvacaryāṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:169": " tat kasya hetoḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:170": " aratayo hy eṣā sarvalokaratayaḥ |māraviṣayâiṣa yad uta kāmaviṣayaniṣevaṇaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:171": " durbuddhisevito hy eṣa mārgaḥ |sarvabuddhivivarṇito hy ayam upadeśaḥ yad uta kāmaniṣevaṇaṃ |ataś câiṣa sarvaduṣkhaskandhasyôtpādâiva niṣevaṇaṃ atâiva ca narakatiryagyoniyamalokānām u-",
    "T04sanss16u:172": " [ Cambridge MS f122b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:173": " tpādaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:174": " kalahabhaṇḍanavivādakṣobhāś ca satvānām atâiva prādurbhavanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:175": " ete ca satvāḥ kāmān niṣevamāṇāḥ buddhānāṃ bhagavatāṃ sakāśād dūrībhavanti",
    "T04sanss16u:176": " svargôpapatter apy ete kāmântarāyāya saṃvartante |",
    "T04sanss16u:177": " kiṃ punar anuttarasya jñānarājasya sarvasatvayogakṣemasya |",
    "T04sanss16u:178": " so 'ham evam apramāṇadoṣān kāmānāṃ paśyan parīttān ādīptāṃs tasmād aham etan nidānam acaraṇatāyāṃ pratipatsye ||",
    "T04sanss16u:179": " pe ||tathā tathâiva mayā kuśalamūlaṃ pariṇāmayitavyaṃ yathā yathâiva",
    "T04sanss16u:180": " sarvasatvâtyantasukham aveditasukhaṃ yāvat sarvajñatāsukhaṃ pratilabheran |",
    "T04sanss16u:181": " mayā sārathinā mayā pariṇāyakena mayôlkādhāriṇā mayā kṣemagatidarśakena",
    "T04sanss16u:182": " [ Bendall ed p282 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:183": " mayā kṣaṇagatipratilabdhena mayôpāyajñena mayârthaviduṣā mayā saṃsārasāgare sarvajñajñānayānapātramahādeśasthitena",
    "T04sanss16u:184": " pariṇāmanakuśalena mayā pāradarśakena ||",
    "T04sanss16u:185": " pe ||",
    "T04sanss16u:186": " na khalu punar asmiṃś cāturmahādvīpake lokadhātau yāvantaḥ satvās tāvantâiva sūryôdāgacchanti cāturdvīpakalokadhātvavabhāsanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:187": " atha ca punar ekâivâiṣāṃ sūryôdāgacchati catu-",
    "T04sanss16u:188": " [ Cambridge MS f123a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:189": " rdvīpâvabhāsanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:190": " na ca teṣāṃ satvānāṃ caturdvīpôpapannānāṃ svakasvakaiḥ śarīrair avabhāsaḥ",
    "T04sanss16u:191": " prādurbhavati |",
    "T04sanss16u:192": " yena te divasasaṃkhyāṃ jānīyuḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:193": " svakāryaṃ vā pariprāpayeyuḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:194": " sasyāni vā paripācayeyuḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:195": " ahar ahar vôdyānanagareṣu ratikrīḍāparibhogam anubhaveyuḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:196": " diśo vā paśyeyuḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:197": " gamanâgamanaṃ vā grāmanagaranigamarāṣṭrarājadhānīṣu kuryuḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:198": " vyavahārakāryeṣu prayujyeran |pe |",
    "T04sanss16u:199": " atha ca punaḥ sūryasya devaputrasyôdayatâikasya sūryamaṇḍalasyâdvitīyasya cāturdvīpake lokadhātau sarvasatvānām avabhāsaḥ prādurbhavati |",
    "T04sanss16u:200": " evam eva bodhisatvasya mahāsatvasya kuśalamūlāny upārpayamānasya kuśalamūlaṃ pariṇāmayamānasyâivaṃ cittam utpadyate |",
    "T04sanss16u:201": " nâiteṣāṃ satvānāṃ tat kuśalamūlaṃ vidyate yena te ātmānaṃ paritrāyeran |",
    "T04sanss16u:202": " kaḥ punar vādaḥ param |",
    "T04sanss16u:203": " ahaṃ punaḥ sarvasatvānāṃ kṛtaśaḥ kuśalamūlāni samudānayāmi kuśalamūlaṃ pariṇāmayāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:204": " yad uta sarvasatvamocanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:205": " sarvasatvānām avabhāsanāya sarvasatvānāṃ jñāpanāya saravsatvānām avatāraṇāya sarvasatvānāṃ parigrahaṇāya sarvasatvānāṃ pariniṣpādanāya sarvasatvānāṃ prasādanāya sarvasatvānāṃ prahlādanāya sarvasatvānāṃ saṃśayacchedanāyâdityamaṇḍalakalpair asmābhir bhavitavyaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:206": " na paraḥ pratikāṅkṣitavyaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:207": " na parasyâvakāśam utpādya satveṣu saṃnāhôtsraṣṭavyaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:208": " na ca sarvasatvānām antikāt sarvasatvatrāṇavyavaśāyo-",
    "T04sanss16u:209": " [ Bendall ed p283 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:210": " nivartayitavyaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:211": " na pariṇāmanāyāḥ sarvaduṣkhahatyā vinivartitavyaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:212": " na parīttāni kuśalamūlāni parigrahītavyāni |",
    "T04sanss16u:213": " na parīttayā pariṇāmanayā tuṣṭir mantavyêty ādi ||",
    "T04sanss16u:214": " āryâkṣayamatisūtre 'py āha |",
    "T04sanss16u:215": " sa na kalpagaṇanayā bodhiṃ paryeṣate |",
    "T04sanss16u:216": " iyataḥ kalpān saṃnatsyāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:217": " iyataḥ kalpān saṃnatsyāmîti |",
    "T04sanss16u:218": " api tu khalv acintyam eva saṃnāhaṃ saṃnahyati |",
    "T04sanss16u:219": " yāvatī pūrvākoṭiḥ saṃsārasya yady etāvad ekaṃ rātriṃdivaṃ bhavet |",
    "T04sanss16u:220": " evaṃrūpai rātriṃdivaiḥ pañcadaśadaivasikena pakṣeṇa triṃśaddaivasikena māsena dvādaśamāsikena saṃvatsareṇânayā varṣagaṇanayā yāvad varṣaśatasahasreṇâikaṃ bodhicittam utpādayeyam ekaṃ ca tathāgatam arhantaṃ samyaksaṃbuddhaṃ paśyeyaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:221": " anena praveśenânayā gaṇanayā gaṅgānadīvālukāsamaiś cittôtpādais",
    "T04sanss16u:222": " tathāgatadarśanaiś câikâikasya",
    "T04sanss16u:223": " [ Cambridge MS f124a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:224": " api satvasya cittacaritaṃ jānīyāṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:225": " anenâiva praveśenânayā gaṇanayā sarvasatvānāṃ tāvadbhiś cittôtpādais",
    "T04sanss16u:226": " tathāgatadarśanaiḥ svacittacaritāni prajanīyām ity anavalīnaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:227": " saṃnāho 'yaṃ bodhisatvasyâkṣayaḥ saṃnāhaḥ |evaṃ dānâdiṣu bodhipākṣikamahāpuruṣalakṣaṇeṣu ca nayaḥ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:228": " āryaratnameghe 'py uktaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:229": " na bodhisatvaḥ satvakhaṭuṅkatāṃ satvadurdāntatāṃ jñātvā |",
    "T04sanss16u:230": " alam ebhiḥ satvair evaṃ khaṭuṅkair evaṃ durdāntair iti |",
    "T04sanss16u:231": " tato nidānaṃ parikhinnaḥ parāpṛṣṭhībhūtaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:232": " pariśuddhāyāṃ lokadhātau praṇidhānaṃ karoti |",
    "T04sanss16u:233": " yatrêdṛśānāṃ satvānāṃ nāmâpi na śṛṇuyāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:234": " na ca satvârthavaimukhyasya bodhisatvapariśuddhāyāṃ lokadhātāv upapattir bhavati |",
    "T04sanss16u:235": " tatra prājño bodhisatvâivaṃ ci-",
    "T04sanss16u:236": " [ Bendall ed p284 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:237": " ttam utpādayati |",
    "T04sanss16u:238": " tasmāt satvadhātor ye satvāḥ syuḥ pratyavarā dhajaḍâiḍamūkajātīyāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:239": " aparinirvāṇadharmakāḥ kṛtsnā satvadhātau na cikitsitāḥ sarvabuddhaiḥ sarvabodhisatvaiś ca pratyākhyātāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:240": " teṣāṃ madīye buddhakṣetre saṃnipātaḥ syāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:241": " tān ahaṃ sarvān bodhimaṇḍe niṣīdyânuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhim abhisaṃbodhayeyaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:242": " evaṃ hi bodhisatvasya cintaya-",
    "T04sanss16u:243": " [ Cambridge MS f124b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:244": " taś cittôtpāde cittôtpāde sarvamārabhavanāni prakampante |",
    "T04sanss16u:245": " sarvabuddhāś câsya varṇavādino bhavantîti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:246": " evaṃ tāvat puṇyavṛddhikāmenâśayo dṛḍhīkartavyaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:247": " āśayadṛḍhīkaraṇârtham adhunôcyate |",
    "T04sanss16u:248": " kiṃ punar anena dṛḍhīkṛtenêti |",
    "T04sanss16u:249": " vimarṣanirāsāya dharmasaṃgītisūtre gaditaṃ |āśaye samyag bhagavan buddhadharmāṇāṃ mūlaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:250": " yasya punar āśayo nâsti sarve buddhadharmās tasya dūre ||",
    "T04sanss16u:251": " āśayasaṃpannasya punar bhagavan yadi buddhā na bhavanti gaganatalād dharmaśabdo niścarati kuḍmavṛkṣebhyaś ca |",
    "T04sanss16u:252": " āśayaśuddhasya bodhisatvasya svamanojalpād eva sarvâvavādânuśāsanyo niścaranti |",
    "T04sanss16u:253": " tasmāt tarhi bhagavan bodhisatvenâśayasaṃpannena bhavitavyaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:254": " tad yathā bhagavan yasya pādau tasya gamanaṃ evaṃ bhagavan yasyâśayas tasya buddhadharmāḥ |tad yathā bhagavan yasyôttamâṅgaṃ tasya jīvitaṃ evam",
    "T04sanss16u:255": " eva bhagavan yasyâśayas tasya buddhabodhiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:256": " tad yathā bhagavan yasya jīvitaṃ tasya lābhaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:257": " evam eva bhagavan yasyâśayas tasya buddhatvalābhaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:258": " tad yathā bhagavan satītvenâgnir jvalati |",
    "T04sanss16u:259": " asatītvena na",
    "T04sanss16u:260": " [ Bendall ed p285 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:261": " jvalati |",
    "T04sanss16u:262": " evam eva bhagavann āśaye sati bodhisatvasya sarvabuddhadharmā jvalanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:263": " asaty āśaye na jva-",
    "T04sanss16u:264": " [ Cambridge MS f125a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:265": " lanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:266": " tad yathā bhagavan satsv abhramegheṣu varṣaṃ varṣaty asatsu na varṣati |",
    "T04sanss16u:267": " evam eva bhagavann āśaye sati buddhadharmāḥ pravartante |",
    "T04sanss16u:268": " tad yathā bhagavan yasya vṛkṣasya mūlaṃ vipannaṃ tasya puṣpaphalāni na bhūyaḥ prarohanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:269": " evam eva bhagavan yasyâśayo vipannas tasya sarve kuśalā dharmā na bhūyaḥ saṃbhavanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:270": " tasmāt tarhi bhagavan bodhisatvena buddhabodhyarthikena svâśayaḥ sûdgṛhītaḥ svārakṣitaḥ suśodhitaḥ svadhiṣṭhitaḥ kartavyêti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:271": " ko 'yam āśayo nāma |",
    "T04sanss16u:272": " āryâkṣayamatisūtre 'bhihitaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:273": " sa khalu punar āśayo 'kṛtrimaḥ akṛtakatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:274": " akṛtako niḥsādhyatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:275": " niḥsādhyaḥ suviditatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:276": " suvidito nirmāyatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:277": " nirmāyaḥ śuddhatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:278": " śuddhaḥ ṛjukatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:279": " ṛjukaḥ akuṭilatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:280": " akuṭilaḥ spaṣṭatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:281": " spaṣṭo 'viṣamatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:282": " aviṣamaḥ sāratvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:283": " sāro 'bhedyatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:284": " abhedyo dṛḍhatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:285": " dṛḍho 'calitatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:286": " acalitâniśritatvād ity ādi |",
    "T04sanss16u:287": " ayam eva câdhikâdhikaguṇâdhigamapravṛtto 'dhyāśayêty ucyate ||",
    "T04sanss16u:288": " yathâtrâivôktaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:289": " uttaraṇâdhyāśayo viśeṣagamanatayêty ādi ||",
    "T04sanss16u:290": " api câdhyāśayôcyate |",
    "T04sanss16u:291": " saumyatā bhūteṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:292": " maitratā satveṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:293": " hitacittatâryeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:294": " kāruṇyam anāryeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:295": " gauravaṃ guruṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:296": " trāṇatâtrāṇeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:297": " śaraṇatâśaraṇeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:298": " dvīpatâdvīpeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:299": " parāyaṇatâparāyaṇeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:300": " sahāyatâsahāyeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:301": " ṛjutā kuṭileṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:302": " spaṣṭatā khaṭuṅkeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:303": " [ Bendall ed p286 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:304": " aśaṭhatā śaṭheṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:305": " amāyâgahanacariteṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:306": " kṛtajñatâkṛtajñeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:307": " kṛtaveditā drohiṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:308": " upakāritânupakāriṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:309": " satyatâbhūtagateṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:310": " nirmānatā śrabdheṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:311": " aninditā su anindanā kṛteṣu [[DOUBT]] |",
    "T04sanss16u:312": " anārocanatā paraskhaliteṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:313": " ārakṣaṇatā vipratipanneṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:314": " adoṣadarśanatā sarvôpāyakauśalyacaryāsu |",
    "T04sanss16u:315": " śuśrūṣaṇatā sarvadakṣiṇīyeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:316": " pradakṣiṇagrāhitânuśāsanīṣv ity ādi ||",
    "T04sanss16u:317": " tad evaṃ vyavasāyâśayau dṛḍhīkṛtya kāruṇyaṃ puraskṛtya yate śubhavṛddhaye ||",
    "T04sanss16u:318": " yathôktam āryadharmasaṃgītisūtre |",
    "T04sanss16u:319": " atha khalv avalokiteśvaro bodhisatvo mahāsatvo bhagavantam etad avocat |",
    "T04sanss16u:320": " na bhagavan bodhisatvenâtibahuṣu dharmeṣu śikṣitavyaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:321": " eko dharmo bhagavan bodhisatvena svārādhitaḥ supratividdhaḥ kartavyaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:322": " tasya sarvabuddhadharmāḥ karatalagatā bhavanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:323": " katamâikadharmo |",
    "T04sanss16u:324": " yad uta mahākaruṇā |",
    "T04sanss16u:325": " mahākaruṇayā bhaga-",
    "T04sanss16u:326": " [ Cambridge MS f126a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:327": " van bodhisatvānāṃ sarvabuddhadharmāḥ karatalagatā bhavanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:328": " tad yathā bhagavan yena rājñaś cakravartinaś cakraratnaṃ gacchati |",
    "T04sanss16u:329": " tena sarvo balakāyo gacchati |",
    "T04sanss16u:330": " evam eva bhagavan yena bodhisatvasya mahākaruṇā gacchati |",
    "T04sanss16u:331": " tena sarve buddhadharmā gacchanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:332": " tad yathā bhagavann āditye udite satvāḥ karmakriyāsu pracurā bhavanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:333": " evam eva bhagavan mahākaruṇā yatrôditā bhavati tatrânyabodhikarā dharmāḥ",
    "T04sanss16u:334": " kriyāsu pracurā bhava-",
    "T04sanss16u:335": " [ Bendall ed p287 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:336": " nti |",
    "T04sanss16u:337": " tad yathā bhagavan sarveṣām indriyāṇāṃ manasâdhiṣṭhitānāṃ svasvaviṣaye grahaṇaprācuryaṃ bhavati",
    "T04sanss16u:338": " evam eva bhagavan mahākaruṇâdhiṣṭhitānām anyeṣāṃ bodhikarāṇāṃ dharmāṇāṃ svasmin svasmin karaṇīye prācuryaṃ bhavati |",
    "T04sanss16u:339": " tad yathā bhagavan jīvitêndriye saty anyeṣām indriyāṇāṃ pravṛttir bhavati",
    "T04sanss16u:340": " evam eva bhagavan mahākaruṇāyāṃ satyām anyeṣāṃ bodhikarāṇāṃ dharmāṇāṃ pravṛttir bhavatîti",
    "T04sanss16u:341": " āryâkṣayamatisūtre 'py āha ||",
    "T04sanss16u:342": " tad yathâpi nāma bhadanta sāradvatīputra puruṣasya jīvitêndriyasyâśvāsāḥ praśvāsāḥ pūrvaṃgamāḥ",
    "T04sanss16u:343": " evam eva bhadanta sāradvatīputra bodhisatvasya mahāyānasamudāgatasya mahākaruṇā pūrvaṃgamāḥ",
    "T04sanss16u:344": " pe ||",
    "T04sanss16u:345": " syād yathâpi nāma śreṣṭhi-",
    "T04sanss16u:346": " [ Cambridge MS f126b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:347": " no vā gṛhapater vâikaputrake guṇavati majjāgataṃ prema |",
    "T04sanss16u:348": " evam eva mahākaruṇāpratilabdhasya bodhisatvasya sarvasatveṣu majjāgataṃ premêti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:349": " katham eṣā bhāvayitavyā |",
    "T04sanss16u:350": " svakam anekavidhaṃ pūrvânubhūtam anubhūyamānaṃ vā duṣkhaṃ bhayaṃ ca svâtmany atyantam aniṣṭaṃ bhāvayitvā |",
    "T04sanss16u:351": " priyâdiṣu maitrī maitrīvatā bhāvayitavyā pratyutpannaduṣkhavyādhiṣu mahāduṣkhasāgarânavadhidīrghasaṃsāravyasanânunīteṣu vā ||",
    "T04sanss16u:352": " yathôktam āryadaśabhūmakasūtre |",
    "T04sanss16u:353": " tasyâivaṃ bhavaty āścaryaṃ yāvad ajñānasaṃmūḍhā vatême bālapṛthagjanāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:354": " yeṣām asaṃkhyeyâtmabhāvā niruddhā nirudhyante nirotsyante ca |",
    "T04sanss16u:355": " evaṃ ca kṣīyamāṇā kāye na nirvedam utpādayanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:356": " bhūyasyā mātrayā duṣkhayantraṃ vivardhayanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:357": " saṃsāraśrotasaś ca mahābhayān na",
    "T04sanss16u:358": " [ Bendall ed p288 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:359": " nivartante |",
    "T04sanss16u:360": " skandhâlayaṃ ca nôtsṛjanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:361": " dhātûragebhyaś ca na nirvidyante |",
    "T04sanss16u:362": " nandīrāgândhāś ca nâvabudhyante |",
    "T04sanss16u:363": " ṣaḍāyatanaśūnyagrāmaṃ ca na vyavalokayanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:364": " ahaṃkāramamakārâbhiniveśânuśayaṃ ca na prajahanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:365": " mānadṛṣṭiśalyaṃ ca nôddharanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:366": " rāgadveṣamohajālaṃ ca na praśamayanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:367": " avidyāmohândhakāraṃ ca na vidhamayanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:368": " tṛṣṇârṇa-",
    "T04sanss16u:369": " [ Cambridge MS f127a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:370": " vaṃ ca nôcchoṣayanti |",
    "T04sanss16u:371": " daśabalasârthavāhaṃ ca na paryeṣante |",
    "T04sanss16u:372": " mārâśayagahanânugatāś ca saṃsārasāgare vividhâkuśalavitarkagrāhâkule pariplavante |",
    "T04sanss16u:373": " apratiśaraṇāḥ tathā saṃvegam āpadyante bahūni duṣkhāni pratyanubhavantaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:374": " yad idaṃ jātijarāvyādhimaraṇaśokaparidevaduṣkhadaurmanasyôpāyāsān |",
    "T04sanss16u:375": " hantâham eṣāṃ satvānāṃ duṣkhârtānām anāthānām atrāṇānām aśaraṇānām alayanānām âparāyaṇānām andhānām avidyâṇḍakoṣapaṭalaparyavanaddhānāṃ tamoabhibhūtānām arthāyâiko 'dvitīyo bhūtvā",
    "T04sanss16u:376": " tathārūpapuṇyajñānasaṃbhārôpacayaṃ bibharmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:377": " yathārūpeṇa puṇyajñānasaṃbhārôpacayena saṃbhṛtenême sarvasatvâbhyantaviśuddhim anuprāpnuyur iti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:378": " tathâtrâivâha |",
    "T04sanss16u:379": " saṃsārâṭavīkāntāramārgaprapannā vatême satvā nirayatiryagyoniyamalokapra-",
    "T04sanss16u:380": " [ Bendall ed p289 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:381": " pātâbhimukhāḥ kudṛṣṭiviṣamajālânuprāptāḥ mohagahanasaṃchannā mithyāmārgavitathaprayātā |",
    "T04sanss16u:382": " andhībhūtāḥ pariṇāyakavikalāḥ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:383": " pe ||",
    "T04sanss16u:384": " saṃsāraśrotânuvāhinaḥ tṛṣṇānadīprapannāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:385": " mahāvegagrastā |",
    "T04sanss16u:386": " avalokanâsamarthāḥ [[DOUBT]] kāmavyāpādavicikitsāvihiṃsāvi-",
    "T04sanss16u:387": " [ Cambridge MS f127b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:388": " tarkaprapātânucaritāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:389": " svakāyadṛṣṭyudakarākṣasagṛhītāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:390": " kāmagahanâvarttânupraviṣṭāḥ nandīrāgamadhyasaṃsaktāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:391": " asmimānasthalôcchannāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:392": " aparāyaṇāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:393": " āyatanagrāmânucchalitāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:394": " kuśalasaṃbhārakavirahitāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:395": " te 'smābhir mahākuśalamūlabalenôddhṛtya nirupadrave 'rajasi",
    "T04sanss16u:396": " śivasarvajñatāratnadvīpe pratiṣṭhāpayitavyā |",
    "T04sanss16u:397": " ruddhā vatême satvā",
    "T04sanss16u:398": " bahuduṣkhadaurmanasyôpāyāsabahulânunayapratighapriyâpriyavinibandhane",
    "T04sanss16u:399": " saśokaparidevânucarite tṛṣṇānigaḍabandhane māyāśāṭhyâvidyāgahanasaṃchanne traidhātukacārake",
    "T04sanss16u:400": " te 'smābhiḥ sarvatraidhātukaviveke 'bhayapure sarvaduṣkhôpaśame [[DOUBT]]",
    "T04sanss16u:401": " anāvaraṇanirvāṇe pratiṣṭhāpayitavyêty ādi ||evam ebhiḥ parasparadṛḍhīkṛtyair vyavasāyâśayakāruṇyaiḥ puṇyavṛddhim ārabhet |",
    "T04sanss16u:402": " tatra tāvad bhadrâcāryāvidhiḥ kāryā vandanâdiḥ sadādarāt ||",
    "T04sanss16u:403": " [ Bendall ed p290 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:404": " āryôgradattaparipṛcchāyāṃ hi trirātre trir divasasya ca śuceḥ",
    "T04sanss16u:405": " śucivastraprāvṛtasya ca triskandhakapravartanam uktaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:406": " tatra trayaḥ skandhāḥ pāpadeśanāpuṇyânumodanābuddhâdhyeṣaṇâ-",
    "T04sanss16u:407": " [ Cambridge MS f128a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:408": " khyāḥ puṇyarāśitvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:409": " tatra vandanā pāpadeśanāyām antarbhavati |",
    "T04sanss16u:410": " buddhān namaskṛtyôpāliparipṛcchāyāṃ deśanêti kṛtvā |",
    "T04sanss16u:411": " yācanam adhyeṣaṇāyāṃ ekârthatvāt |",
    "T04sanss16u:412": " pūjā tu vibhavâbhāvād anityêti nôktā |",
    "T04sanss16u:413": " mānasī vācasī ca sūtrântaraprasiddhatvān nôktāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:414": " trayāṇāṃ tu vacanāt prādhānyaṃ gamyate |",
    "T04sanss16u:415": " tatra vandanā |",
    "T04sanss16u:416": " sarvabuddhān namasyāmîti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:417": " āryâkṣayamatisūtre tv ātmaparapāpadeśanā puṇyasaṃbhāre paṭhyate ||",
    "T04sanss16u:418": " gāthācatuṣṭayena ca yathāgītaiś ca stotraiḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:419": " āryabhadracaryâdigāthābhir vā pūjanā ca ||",
    "T04sanss16u:420": " āryaratnameghe yathôktaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:421": " iha bodhisatvo yānîmāni bhavanti puṣpajātāni vā phalajātāni vâmamāny aparigrahāṇi |",
    "T04sanss16u:422": " tāni triṣkṛtvā rātrau triṣkṛtvā divase buddhabodhisatvebhyo niryātayati ||",
    "T04sanss16u:423": " pe ||",
    "T04sanss16u:424": " sayathîme [[DOUBT]] dhūpavṛkṣā vā gandhavṛkṣā vā ratnavṛkṣā vā kalpavṛkṣā vâmamâparigrahās tān api triṣkṛtvā rātrau triṣkṛtvā divase buddhabodhisatvebhyo niryātayatîti ||āryatrisamayarāje 'pi sthalajā ratnaparvatāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:425": " jalajā ratnaparvatā sthalajalajāni ratnāni daśadigavasthitāni |",
    "T04sanss16u:426": " amamāny aparigrahāṇi deyānîty uktaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:427": " anayā ca diśā sarvabhaiṣajyā-",
    "T04sanss16u:428": " [ Bendall ed p291 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:429": " ni sarvarasāyanāni sarvasalilāni a-",
    "T04sanss16u:430": " [ Cambridge MS f128b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:431": " navadyāni apmaṇḍalāni |",
    "T04sanss16u:432": " sarvakāñcanamaṇḍalāni |",
    "T04sanss16u:433": " vivṛtteṣu vā lokadhātuṣu ye paramarasasparśasaṃpannā bhūparpaṭakāḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:434": " amṛtalatā |",
    "T04sanss16u:435": " akṛṣṭôptā vā śālayaḥ |",
    "T04sanss16u:436": " sarvôttarakurudvīpeṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:437": " pariśuddheṣu ca lokadhātuṣu ye ramaṇīyatarāḥ paribhogāḥ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:438": " yathā câryaratnameghe evâha |",
    "T04sanss16u:439": " sa yānîmāni sūtrânteṣûdārôdārāṇi tathāgatapūjôpasthānāni śṛṇoti |",
    "T04sanss16u:440": " tāny āśayatas tīvreṇâdhyāśayena buddhabodhisatvebhyaḥ pariṇāmayatîti |",
    "T04sanss16u:441": " tathā |",
    "T04sanss16u:442": " sa vividhāni pūjôpasthānāni anuvicintayatîti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:443": " deśanā pūrvôktêva |",
    "T04sanss16u:444": " āryâkṣayamatisūtre tv ātmaparapāpadeśanā puṇyasaṃbhāre paṭhyate |",
    "T04sanss16u:445": " anumodanā bhadracaryāgāthayā |",
    "T04sanss16u:446": " candrapradīpânumodanāparivartena vā |",
    "T04sanss16u:447": " adhyeṣaṇā bhadracaryayâiva |",
    "T04sanss16u:448": " pariṇāmanā tu sakalasamāptâryabhadracaryayâiva |",
    "T04sanss16u:449": " vajradhvajapariṇāmanāṃ vā paśyet ||athavā daśabhūmakôktāni",
    "T04sanss16u:450": " mahāpraṇidhānāni |",
    "T04sanss16u:451": " yathâha |",
    "T04sanss16u:452": " yad utâśeṣaniḥśeṣânavaśeṣasarvabuddhapūjôpasthāpanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:453": " sarvâkāravarôpetam udārâdhimuktiviśuddhaṃ dharmadhātuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ sarvakalpasaṃkhyābuddhôtpādasaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:454": " mahāpūjôpasthā-",
    "T04sanss16u:455": " [ Bendall ed p292 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:456": " nāya",
    "T04sanss16u:457": " [ Cambridge MS f129a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:458": " prathamaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati || yad uta sarvatathāgatabhāṣitadharmanetrīsaṃdhāraṇāya sarvabuddhabodhisatvaparigrahāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:459": " sarvasamyaksaṃbuddhaśāsanaparirakṣaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:460": " dharmadhātuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:461": " sarvasaṃkalpasaṃkhyābuddhôtpādasaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:462": " saddharmaparigrahāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:463": " dvitīyaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati ||",
    "T04sanss16u:464": " yad uta sarvabuddhôtpādaniravaśeṣasarvalokadhātuprasareṣu |",
    "T04sanss16u:465": " tuṣitabhavanavāsam ādiṃ kṛtvā",
    "T04sanss16u:466": " cyavanâcaṅkramaṇagarbhasthitijanmakumārakrīḍântaḥpuravāsâbhiniṣkramaṇaduṣkaracaryābodhimaṇḍôpasaṃkramaṇamāradharṣaṇâbhisaṃbodhyadhyeṣaṇamahādharmacakrapravartanamahāparinirvāṇôpasaṃkramaṇāya",
    "T04sanss16u:467": " pūjādharmasaṃgrahaprayogapūrvaṃgamaṃ kṛtvā sarvatraikālavivartanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:468": " dharmadhātuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:469": " sarvakalpasaṃkhyābuddhôtpādasaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ yāvan",
    "T04sanss16u:470": " mahāparinirvāṇôpasaṃkramaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:471": " tṛtīyaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati ||",
    "T04sanss16u:472": " yad uta sarvabodhisatvacaryāvipulamahadgatâpramāṇâsaṃbhinnasarvapāramitāsusaṃgrahītaḥ",
    "T04sanss16u:473": " sarvabhūmipariśodhanaṃ sâṅgôpāṅganirhāraṃ yāvat sala-",
    "T04sanss16u:474": " [ Cambridge MS f129b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:475": " kṣaṇavilakṣaṇasaṃvartavivartasarvabodhi satvacaryābhūtayathāvad bhūmipathôpadeśapāramitāparikarmâvavādânuśāsany-anupradānôpasta-",
    "T04sanss16u:476": " [ Bendall ed p293 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:477": " mbhacittôtpādâbhinirhārāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:478": " dharmadha-tuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ sarvakalpasaṃkhyācaryāsaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ cittôtpādâbhinirhārāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:479": " caturthaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati || yad uta niravaśeṣasarvasatvadhāturūpyarūpisaṃjñāsaṃjñi nâiva saṃjñi nâsaṃjñy",
    "T04sanss16u:480": " aṇḍajajarāyujasaṃsvedajâupapādukatraidhātukaparyāpannaṣaḍgatisamavasṛtasarvôpapattiparyāpannanāmarūpasaṃgṛhītâśeṣasarvasatvadhātuparipācanāya",
    "T04sanss16u:481": " sarvabuddhadharmâvatāraṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:482": " sarvagatisaṃkhyāvyavacchedanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:483": " sarvajñajñānapratiṣṭhāpanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:484": " dharmadhātu-",
    "T04sanss16u:485": " [ Cambridge MS f130a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:486": " vipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:487": " sarvakalpasaṃkhyāsatvadhātusaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:488": " |sarvasatvadhātuparipācanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:489": " pañcamaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati ||",
    "T04sanss16u:490": " yad uta niravaśeṣasarvalokadhātuvipulasaṃkṣiptamahadgatâpramāṇasūkṣmâudārikavyatyastâvamūrddhasamatalapraveśasamavasaraṇânugatêndrajālavibhāgadaśadigaśeṣavaimātryapraveśavibhāgajñānânugamapratyakṣatāyai",
    "T04sanss16u:491": " dharmadhātuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ sarvakalpasaṃkhyālokadhātusaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ lokadhātuvaimātryâvatāraṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:492": " ṣaṣṭhaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati ||",
    "T04sanss16u:493": " yad uta sarvakṣetrâikakṣetrâikakṣetra sarvakṣetraisamavaśaraṇapariśodhanaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:494": " apramāṇabuddhakṣetra prabhāvyūhâlaṃkārapratimaṇḍitaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:495": " sarvakleśâpanayanapariśuddhipathôpetaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:496": " apramāṇajñānâkārasatvaparipūrṇam udārabuddhaviṣayasamavasaraṇaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:497": " yathâśayasarvasatvasaṃdarśanasaṃtoṣaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:498": " dharmadhātuvi-",
    "T04sanss16u:499": " [ Bendall ed p294 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:500": " pulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:501": " |sarvakalpasaṃkhyābuddhakṣetrasaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ",
    "T04sanss16u:502": " |sarvabuddhakṣetrapariśodhanāya |saptamaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati ||yad uta sarvabodhisatvâikâśayaprayogatāyai",
    "T04sanss16u:503": " niḥsapatnakuśalamūlôpacayāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:504": " ekârambaṇasarvabodhisatvasamatāyai |",
    "T04sanss16u:505": " avirahitasatatasamitabuddhabodhisatvasamavadhānāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:506": " yathêṣṭabuddhôtpādasaṃdarśanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:507": " svacittôtpādatathāgataprabhāvajñānânugamāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:508": " acyutânugāminy-abhijñāpratilambhāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:509": " sarvalokadhātvanuvicaraṇāya sarvaparṣanmaṇḍalapratibhāsaprāptaye |",
    "T04sanss16u:510": " sarvôpapattisvaśarīrânugamāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:511": " acintyamahāyānôpetatāyai |",
    "T04sanss16u:512": " [ Cambridge MS f130b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:513": " bodhisatvacaryācaraṇâvyavacchedāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:514": " dharmadhātuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:515": " sarvakalpasaṃkhyācaryāsaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:516": " mahāyānâvatāraṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:517": " aṣṭamaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati ||yad",
    "T04sanss16u:518": " utâvivartyacakrasamārūḍhabodhisatvacaryācaraṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:519": " amoghakāyavāṅmanaskareṇa |",
    "T04sanss16u:520": " sahadarśananiyatasarvabuddhadharmapratilambhāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:521": " sahaghoṣôdāhārajñānâ-",
    "T04sanss16u:522": " [ Bendall ed p295 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:523": " nugamāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:524": " sahaprasādakleśavivartanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:525": " mahābhaiṣajyarājôpamâśrayapratilambhāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:526": " cintāmaṇivat kāyapratilambhāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:527": " sarvabodhisatvacaryācaraṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:528": " dharmadhātuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:529": " sarvakalpasaṃkhyācaryāsaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ |amoghaghoṣatāyai |",
    "T04sanss16u:530": " navamaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharati ||",
    "T04sanss16u:531": " yad uta sarvalokadhātuṣv anuttarasamyaksaṃbodhyabhisaṃbodhanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:532": " ekavālapathâvyativṛttasarvabālapṛthagjanajanmôpapattyabhiniṣkramaṇavikurvaṇa",
    "T04sanss16u:533": " bodhimaṇḍadharmacakrapravartanamahāparinirvāṇôpadarśanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:534": " mahābuddhaviṣayaprabhāvajñānânugamāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:535": " sarvasatvadhātuyathâśayabuddhôtpādakṣaṇakṣaṇâvabodhapraśamaprāpaṇasaṃdarśanāya",
    "T04sanss16u:536": " e-",
    "T04sanss16u:537": " [ Cambridge MS f131a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:538": " kâbhisaṃbodhisarvadharmadhātunirmāṇaspharaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:539": " ekaghoṣôdāhārasarvasatvacittâśayasaṃtoṣaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:540": " mahāparinirvāṇôpadarśanacaryābalâvyupacchedāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:541": " mahājñānabhūmisarvadharmavyutthāpanasaṃdarśanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:542": " dharmajñānaṛddhimāyâbhijñāsarvalokadhātuspharaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:543": " dharmadhātuvipulam ākāśadhātuparyavasānam aparântakoṭīniṣṭhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:544": " sarvakalpasaṃkhyâbhisaṃbodhisaṃkhyāpratiprasrabdhaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:545": " mahāyānâbhinirhārāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:546": " daśamaṃ mahāpraṇidhānam abhinirharatîti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:547": " [ Bendall ed p296 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:548": " etac ca bhāvayan sarvatra pariṇāmayāmîti yojyaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:549": " āryâvalokiteśvaravimokṣe ca yad uktaṃ tad apy evaṃ yojyaṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:550": " etat kuśalamūlaṃ sarvasatvaprapātabhayavigamāya pariṇāmayāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:551": " sarvasatvān sāntānikabhayapraśamanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:552": " sarvasatvasaṃmohabhayavinivartanāya pariṇāmayāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:553": " sarvasatvabandhanabhayasamucchedāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:554": " sarvasatvajīvitôparodhôpakramabhayavyāvartanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:555": " sarvasatvôpakaraṇavaikalyabhayâpanayanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:556": " sarvasatvâjīvikābhayavyupaśamanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:557": " sarvasatvâślokabhayasamatikramaṇāya pariṇāmayāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:558": " sarvasatvasāṃsārikabhayôpaśamanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:559": " sarvasatvaparṣacchāradyabhayavigamāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:560": " sarvasatvamaraṇa-",
    "T04sanss16u:561": " [ Cambridge MS f131b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:562": " bhayavyatikramāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:563": " sarvasatvadurgatibhayavinivartanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:564": " sarvasatvatamoandhakāraviṣamagatyapratyudāvartanâvabhāsakaraṇāya pariṇāmayāmi |",
    "T04sanss16u:565": " sarvasatvānāṃ visabhāgasamavadhānabhayâbhyantavigamāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:566": " sarvasatvapriyaviprayogabhayanirodhāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:567": " sarvasatvâpriyasaṃvāsabhayâpanayanāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:568": " sarvasatvakāyaparipīḍābhayavisaṃyogāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:569": " sarvasatvacittaparipīḍanabhayanirmokṣaṇāya |",
    "T04sanss16u:570": " sarvasatvaduṣkhadaurmanasyôpāyāsasamatikramaṇāya pariṇāmayāmîti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:571": " [ Bendall ed p297 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss16u:572": " saṃkṣepataḥ punar iyam anuttarā pariṇāmanā yêyam āryabhadracaryāgāthāyāṃ |",
    "T04sanss16u:573": " mañjuśirī yatha jānati śūraḥ so ca samantata bhadra tathâiva |",
    "T04sanss16u:574": " teṣu ahaṃ anuśikṣayamāṇo nāmayamī kuśalaṃ imu sarvaṃ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:575": " sarvatriyadhva gatebhi jinebhir yā pariṇāmana varṇitâgrā |",
    "T04sanss16u:576": " tāyâhaṃ kuśalaṃ imu sarvaṃ nāmayamī varabhadracarīye |",
    "T04sanss16u:577": " iti ||",
    "T04sanss16u:578": " iti śikṣāsamuccaye bhadracaryāvidhiḥ ṣoḍaśamaḥ paricchedaḥ samāptaḥ ||",
    "T04sanss16u:579": " Copyright (c) 2002 by Jens Braarvig - Oslo"
}